thread.title: Nanette

author: Nanette
title: Nanette
text:
I ordered 2 pawpaw trees last year but too late to plant. I received an email confirming my order & that my trees would be delivered at the best planting time in 2017. Sure enough! Living in Virginia Beach, my trees arrived a couple of weeks ago. Both arrived in excellent condition.
I will definitely order more trees from Willis Orchards in the future.
